entries.femaleVariant: <mothertongue l="mex" m="chica" b="Don't come here often, do ya? Heheh. It's good to see you, " a="."/>
entries.maleVariant: <mothertongue l="mex" m="cabrón" b="Don't come here often, do ya? Heheh. It's good to see you, " a="."/>

entries.femaleVariant: [Sit] It's good to see you, too.
Mhm... Mhm...
Full-crew job, for sure... A techie, maybe two... a 'runner with a gold-plated brain... an' a driver with wheels from hell…
Not to mention – a solo.
Mhm. The piece I'm missing.
entries.maleVariant: Huh. The piece I'm missing.

entries.femaleVariant: That what you need from me? My trigger finger to zero this lady?
Those're the rules, Jack. You wanna be top, y'gotta have some skin in the game.
entries.maleVariant: Those're the rules, Jack. You wanna be top, gotta have some skin in the game.

entries.femaleVariant: Those are the rules.
<mothertongue l="mex" m="Un pacto con el diablo." b="" a=" Been sayin' it all along. Sold your soul to those Arasaka fuckers."/>
[Raise toast] To this.
To this.
Now, whaddaya say we liquor up and talk life.
Think I have a choice?
Think I have a choice? If I refuse, they take everything and leave me nothing.
entries.maleVariant: Think I have a choice? If I refuse, they take everything and leave me nothin'.

entries.femaleVariant: <mothertongue l="mex" m="pendeja" b="Yeah, but you're not on top – Saburo Arasaka is. And you're the " a=" who keeps him there."/>
entries.maleVariant: <mothertongue l="mex" m="pendejo" b="Yeah, but you're not on top – Saburo Arasaka is. And you're the " a=" who keeps him there."/>

entries.femaleVariant: Yeah, well let 'em. They'll also take the fist they got grippin' your balls.
You'll always be within reach. Always re--
V. Is that right?
Your access to company networks is hereby revoked.
Give us the data you received from Jenkins. This will conclude termination procedures.
Ugh, information's on the shard.
entries.maleVariant: Information's on the shard.

entries.femaleVariant: No, thanks.
You know I don't drink.
With the formalities, yes. But I think Abernathy would gladly up our fee for ridding her of piece of rot like you.
Come on, move it.
<kiroshi l="mex" o="Vaya, esperen." t="Whoa, hold on." b="" a=""/>
Is that a threat?
We have what we came for. It'll do for now.
<mothertongue l="mex" m="Hijo de la chingada..." b="Phew, dodged one there. " a=""/>
Welcome to Lizzie's.
Thought I could count on you.
Delicate situation, I know. That's why I need somebody I can trust.
Thought I could always count on you, Jack…
I need someone I can trust.
Now siddown and tell me what's got your shorts in a knot.
Hagh, you know me, I'm not all sunshine and rainbows, but... this job ain't my style.
Actually, I didn't think it was yours, either.
<mothertongue l="mex" m="hermana" b="This ain't no \"delicate situation,\" " a=". It's a hitjob, plain an' simple."/>
entries.maleVariant: <mothertongue l="mex" m="hermano" b="This ain't no \"delicate situation,\" " a=". It's a hitjob, plain an' simple."/>

entries.femaleVariant: This isn't a professional request I can refuse.
You know how Arasaka operates... Or, OK, maybe you don't.
But I can. And I am. And you should, too.
Was that a toast? The hell does that even mean?

<mothertongue l="mex" m="mamá" b="You raise a glass to your " a=", your <Rich color=\"MainColors.ActiveBlue\">hermana</>. To the <Rich color=\"MainColors.ActiveBlue\">mamacita</> you'll meet at the bar. But \"this\" – doesn't say a damn thing."/>
Sheesh. "To this."
You still never bend the rules, huh?
Hey, OK, I getcha.
This job and all the rest of that corpo bullshit – y'know what it is?
Today, they got you to zero somebody. Tomorrow, they'll get somebody else to zero you.
<mothertongue l="mex" m="matones" b="I dunno 'bout you, but I'm pretty picky about who I let touch my balls. And Saburo and his " a="? Oh, they definitely do not make the cut."/>
Maybe someday. But for now, I'm still well within their reach.
Work for yourself, live for yourself. That's the only way.
Don't believe we've met.
Did Jenkins send you? Don't believe I know you.
You're from Arasaka HQ. Er, is there a problem? Are you here about Frankfurt?
entries.maleVariant: You're from Arasaka HQ. Is there a problem? Are you here about Frankfurt?

entries.femaleVariant: You're from headquarters.
You don't. But we know you very well.
Hey, you lost? Got a problem?
We're here for you.
Jenkins assigned you a task today. You'll share all the details with us.
Who are you again?
Name and department, again? Didn't quite catch it the first time around.
entries.maleVariant: Name and department, again? Didn't quite catch it first time around.

entries.femaleVariant: No, don't believe I will. That's between me and Jenkins.
Task's not your concern.
Hgh, how the hell did you find out?
That is not your concern.
The data. Now.
We done?
In two minutes, any company cybernetics in your possession will cease functioning.
How'd you find out?
I think you fellas mighta forgotten just how far from home you are.
<mothertongue l="mex" m="barrio" b="Not sure this " a="'s your style, let alone a healthy option. <Rich color=\"MainColors.ActiveBlue\">¿Queda claro?</>"/>
Well, you start shootin', maybe we join in, huh? Before you know it, somebody might die today.
Stand up, you're comin' with us.
That, mh... That'd be that, Jack. Just lost control of my life, completely…
entries.maleVariant: That... that'd be that, Jack. Just lost control of my life, completely…

entries.femaleVariant: I'd say you got it back.
You couldn't say "no" to 'em, so they said it to you. This is a turn for the better, you'll see.
Datashard – take it.
It's good to see you, too, Jack. How ya been?
[Hand over datashard] Have a glance.
This needs to stay between us.
Got sparks flyin' between the Valentino boys and Maelstrom. Eddies there for the takin'... as long as ya don't get flatlined.
Jackie, before I start... this stays between us.
<kiroshi l="mex" o="Por supuesto." t="Of course." b="" a=""/>
I'm serious... This thing, it… it could ruin me.
entries.maleVariant: I'm serious... This thing, it could ruin me.

entries.femaleVariant: So could I. You do realize who you're talkin' to, right? A guy who's done this before.
I know, you saved my ass. If word about the cartels had gotten out...
But it didn't, and this won't either. It's why you came to see dear old Jackie.
Remember what happened in México, at the border? I peep one word…
Whaddaya think?
Lemme hear about this problem o' yours.
Double tequila with grenadine and lime. Nothin' better for drownin' nerves.
Smart choice.
V, how you feel? You all right?
Like shit...
Like, argh... Like shit, agh…
entries.maleVariant: Like, ugh... Like shit…

entries.femaleVariant: I... Agh, I can't breathe...
I... I can't...
Need help?
N-no... It's just, agh... withdrawal syndrome... Ugh, sort of…
entries.maleVariant: N-no, no... It's just... withdrawal syndrome... Sort of…

entries.femaleVariant: Think they cut off my hormone regulators, biomon and sat-analysis system... Body's got to adjust…
<mothertongue l="mex" m="primito" b="It's like when my little " a=" was ditchin' drugs. Nasty chills, tremblin' hands, a cold sweat and dry heavin'…"/>
Ye-yeah... Sounds about right...
Won't come cheap. And it'll have to be done on the sly — no trail, hard eddies only.
Got the money.
Ugh, my throat's like sandpaper... Not sure I can breathe…
entries.maleVariant: My throat's like sandpaper... N-not sure I can breathe…

entries.femaleVariant: 'Sides, ya haven't lost everything.
About to say I--I still have a friend? That's sweet.
Still have a friend?
No, Jack, I did... Lost everything... Access to intel systems, my pad, car, contacts... every shred of credibility.
No, Jack, I did... I lost everything.
Haha, no… dumbass. Y'still got that wad for the hit job, don'tcha?
Umh. Least you still got the eddies for the hitjob.
Probably some fat-ass chunk o' cha-ching. Just right for a new start.
<mothertongue l="mex" m="chica" b="That's right, " a=". Buckle up."/>
entries.maleVariant: That's right, fool. Buckle up.

entries.femaleVariant: We have arrived at your destination.
Eh, you know how it is, can't complain, but... we ain't here to shoot the shit about me.
Hey, hey, should I get you to a ripper?
TT policy's gone, Jack... so're my biochem controllers, company pad... I mean, they have seized my bank account. Not frozen – seized!
entries.maleVariant: TT policy's gone, Jack... so're my biochem controllers, company pad... I mean, they've seized my bank account. Not frozen – seized!

entries.femaleVariant: Just need to catch my breath.
Or, I guess, maybe Trauma Team's on its way…
I've lost everything.
Jesus, these fuckers move fast!
You sure you feel OK, though? I mean--
Gimme a minute,ugh, get my shit together…
entries.maleVariant: Gimme a minute, get my shit together…

entries.femaleVariant: Fuck's your problem, psychosuit?!
[Attack]
Seems trouble wants in.
Couldn't use the front door like everyone else?
Just here on business.
Keep an eye on the AV.
I'm in a hurry.
Keep an eye on the AV.
Keep an eye on the AV for me, will ya?
I don't want any trouble – just here on business.
Good to hear.
Listen, I'm in a hurry, and you're wasting my time.
entries.maleVariant: Listen, I'm in a hurry, and you're wastin' my time.

entries.femaleVariant: Gonna keep an eye on you.
This look like a landin' pad to you? Coulda fuckin' crushed us!
Outta my way.
Wha--? Who the fuck're you to say that to me?
Arasaka Counterintel. We done here?
Teh, yeah, yeah...
entries.maleVariant: Heh, yeah, yeah...

entries.femaleVariant: Pff. I don't get paid to do that.
I wasn't asking. And not a scratch on it when I get back.
<kiroshi l="mex" o="Gracias, mamita." t="Thanks, babe." b="" a=""/>
Jesus Christ...
OK, no no, hey, w-we ain't lookin' for no beef witchoo!
Lookin' for your choom? Already here, tappin' his fingers, waitin' for ya.
Ey, you hearin' all right? Don't look so hot.
You expecting something?
Well...? Don't got all day.
What the fuck you doin'?
[Surrender shard] It's all here.
I'm waiting.
The data. Immediately.
[Throw ball]
[Get out]
<mothertongue l="mex" m="hermana" b="Hey, " a=". Your new life... it starts now."/>
entries.maleVariant: <mothertongue l="mex" m="hermano" b="Hey, " a=". Your new life... it starts now."/>

entries.femaleVariant: V, you still with me...?
You there? All OK?
<mothertongue l="mex" m="Ándale" b="" a=", let's drink."/>
The data from Jenkins – I'm waiting.
Fuuuck…
Corpos... fucking do whatever, think the world's theirs.
Used to be our 'hood, this.
Gah, fuck…
How you feelin'? Pretty sharp dive, huh?
